FAQ (Frequently Asked Questions)
========

Q. I can't connect to the database!
++++++++
Confirm that users and permissions are properly configured in the MySQL
database.

Verify that  "testdb.user" and "testdb.pwd" is  correctly specified in
conf/my.build.properties as per your Mysql environment.

Q. I want a faster build
++++++++
If you want to skip running the junit tests, you can do so with:

    ant war 

Q. How do I stop Tomcat?
++++++++
Hit CTRL-C.
